Q. Have you any particular reason for recollecting that he was in your company this day. - A. Yes, I recollect the prisoner was reading the paper;
Emma Reynolds
, the servant of the house, asked me what day of the month it was, the prisoner told her it was the 14th; Emma gave half a pint of gin and bitters because it was her birth day; it was four weeks ago last Saturday.
